### ========== VIDEO API TESTS (Task 1.4) ==========

### 1. Create Video (Basic)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/videos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "dQw4w9WgXcQ"
}

### 2. Create Video with Metadata
POST http://localhost:5000/api/videos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "aircAruvnKk",
  "fetchMetadata": true
}

### 3. Create Video with Metadata and Transcript
POST http://localhost:5000/api/videos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "aircAruvnKk",
  "fetchMetadata": true,
  "fetchTranscript": true,
  "languageCodes": ["en"]
}

### 4. Create Video from URL
POST http://localhost:5000/api/videos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "fetchMetadata": true
}

### 5. Get Video with All Cached Data
GET http://localhost:5000/api/videos/aircAruvnKk

### 6. Get Video Metadata (no cache)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/videos/dQw4w9WgXcQ/metadata

### 7. Get Video Metadata (with cache)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/videos/dQw4w9WgXcQ/metadata?cache=true
